  "instructions": [
    "Heat a tablespoon of oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the tamarind paste and bhuna masala powder to create a thick sauce.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and grated ginger until fragrant.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk, bring to simmer, then add salt for taste balance.",
    "Slice bell peppers, red onions, and shiitake mushrooms. Add them into the pan and cook until they start to soften.",
    "Garnish with fresh basil leaves and crushed thyme for added flavor and presentation.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or main course."
